    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person\u2014it is in absolutely pristine condition! It\u2019s been babied since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The paint is flawless, the interior is totally spotless, and it drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely fall in love with it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
