      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level 996.2 Carrera 4S in impeccable mechanical and cosmetic order. This specimen features the naturally aspirated 3.6L flat-six mated to a G96/01 6-speed manual transaxle. Critical preventative maintenance is fully documented, including an LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recent rear main seal replacement. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, utilizing the Turbo-derived wide-body suspension geometry and four-piston monobloc Brembo calipers over cross-drilled rotors. The viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system operates flawlessly, providing optimal torque distribution. Zero bore scoring confirmed via recent scope; the M96 power plant exhibits perfect compression across all cylinders. This is a turn-key, collector-grade example with a dry underbody and pristine original paint depth.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
