    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle in showroom-fresh condition. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating; there are zero rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, retaining its original factory scent. The premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear or creasing, and the high-gloss interior trim is free of any micro-scratching. Every technological feature, sensor, and button operates with the tactile precision of a new car. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance history performed exclusively by certified technicians. The vehicle comes with a complete set of service records, both original key fobs, the owner\u2019s manual, and the original window sticker. This is a turn-key example for a buyer who refuses to compromise on quality.",
